{"tid":2344554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠嘅你，而家做緊咩？(圍爐區)","createTime":"2020-12-28T22:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T23:12:33.000Z","uid":364562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c457dd45cb04a96f1290cac92a867e4f447295","tid":2344554,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:44:30.000Z","msg":"入黎取下暖<br />\n而排發生左好多野<br />\n個人好灰<br />\n想人生活得積極啲<br />\n<br />\n發覺越係諗得長遠<br />\n人就越焦慮<br />\n<br />\n而家開始唔諗將來<br />\n比自己休息下<br />\n諗下一陣早餐食咩"},{"pid":"c998421e0887597824d33c61e17e74b1324664d8","tid":2344554,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:50:23.000Z","msg":"香港生活好急<br />\n咩都要快，搞到個人好焦慮<br />\n<br />\n其實慢又有咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n做人最緊要開心"},{"pid":"f65f586fc653f534553f484ae9c490216a654734","tid":2344554,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:52:58.000Z","msg":"健康定義<br />\n生理，心理，社交<br />\n<br />\n做左幾年野好似已經失去哂<br />\n<br />\n係時候要搵返哂佢哋反嚟"},{"pid":"095a4d1789f4413afde40da9dcfca1b4cda5a339","tid":2344554,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a627c40db8c5b2ce29c76ac298ffb59bdfb2e63d","tid":2344554,"uid":172770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T22:58:41.000Z","msg":"不如講下發生咗咩？<br />\n幫就一定幫你唔到<br />\n不過可以聽你吐下苦水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c6b3d2ec29353696b4e3b2f05813e34c2777e0","tid":2344554,"uid":87043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:11:29.000Z","msg":"加油.！"},{"pid":"7427f430a10bee44928520140791b55e54457bc8","tid":2344554,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T23:12:49.000Z","msg":"返工返到無哂時間同朋友相處<br />\n做到個人五勞七傷<br />\n最近又比人屌做得差<br />\n個人好崩潰<br />\n<br />\n想搵人傾下計先發現無哂朋友<br />\n<br />\n其實唔關人地事<br />\n係自己太過投入工作<br />\n忽略哂身邊所有人<br />\n<br />\n走頭無路唯有上連登訴心聲"},{"pid":"7fcaff614294ea4fa6caafc0f545